name: Deeproot Champion
oracle_text: Whenever you cast a noncreature spell, put a +1/+1 counter on Deeproot Champion.
flavor_text: "No good will come from what you seek. Turn back now or suffer an ignoble death far from your home."

name: Noggle Bandit
oracle_text: Noggle Bandit can't be blocked except by creatures with defender.
flavor_text: Noggles believe that they were the first race ever to walk Shadowmoor. They don't "steal." They just take back what's rightfully theirs.

name: Armory Guard
oracle_text: Armory Guard has vigilance as long as you control a Gate.
flavor_text: The Dimir agents watched from the shadows. "Eight hours, and I've yet to see him blink," Nefara hissed. "I suggest we find another way in."

oracle_text:
Sacrifice three white creatures: Exile target creature.
Whenever another black creature you control dies, create a 1/1 white Spirit creature token with flying.
flavor_text: "Spend your life betraying me if you wish. I'll simply take it up with your ghost."

oracle_text:
You can't cast this spell if you've played a land this turn.
You can't play lands if you've cast Rock Jockey this turn.
flavor_text: Goblins don't know much about physics, but they know lots about falling and rocks.

Wild Nacatl gets +1/+1 as long as you control a Plains.

Flying

oracle_text:
Flying
